title: Kersgieter, Chatzileonti put Kansas women over Ga Tech 77-58 - The Associated Press - en Español
content: Kersgieter, Chatzileonti put Kansas women over Ga Tech 77-58  The Associated Press - en Español
description: STANFORD, Calif. (AP) — Once Kansas set its mind on not getting outhustled for even one more possession, the Jayhawks took over.  Ioanna Chatzileonti had 15 points and 10 rebounds, Holly Kersgieter scored 19 points and eighth-seeded Kansas beat ninth-seeded Georgia Tech 77-58 on Friday night in the first round of the NCAA Tournament.
